sections.heading: Security, Privacy, and Dissemination of Criminal History Information Act, how cited
sections.text: Sections 29-209, 29-210, 29-3501 to 29-3528, and 81-1423 shall be known and may be cited as the Security, Privacy, and Dissemination of Criminal History Information Act.SourceLaws 1978, LB 713, ยง 1.
